
This directory contains programs donated by Guna Seetharaman, The Center for
Advanced Computer Studies, University of Southwestern Louisiana
(CSNet: guna@usl.usl.edu).

hips2imP.c:
	
	This program converts a HIPS image to ImPress format for printing on
various Imagen laser printers.  To compile:

		cc -o hips2imP hips2imP.c -lhips

slant.c

	This program performs the forward and inverse slant transforms.  The
resulting image is after both the forward and inverse transforms have been
applied, but you can easily extract the code for the separate transforms if
you need to work with the transformed image.  To compile:

		cc -o slant slant.c -lhips -lm
